{"about_the_game":"<strong>Football Life Simulator</strong> is a unique simulation game that lets you experience the life of a football player, both on and off the field. As you embark on a professional football career, you'll also need to manage your social life. Bar outings, car collections, friendships, and romantic relationships are just a few of the social activities awaiting you in this game. At the same time, you'll train with your teams, play matches, and climb the career ladder, developing your football skills and realizing that the more you earn, the more you need to spend.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158270/extras/1Improve2.png?t=1733759654\" /><br>Improve your football skills through realistic training mini-games and shine on the pitch with your abilities.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158270/extras/Gif1Training.gif?t=1733759654\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158270/extras/2Work2.png?t=1733759654\" /><br>Run on the treadmill, lift weights, and challenge yourself by boosting your strength and stamina.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158270/extras/GifGym2.gif?t=1733759654\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158270/extras/3Enjoy.png?t=1733759654\" /><br>Manage social activities like bar outings, friendships, and romantic relationships, and enjoy your free time.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158270/extras/GifBar.gif?t=1733759654\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158270/extras/4Hero.png?t=1733759654\" /><br>Show off your skills in matches, turn opportunities into goals, excite the fans, and rise in your career.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158270/extras/GifMatch.gif?t=1733759654\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158270/extras/5More.png?t=1733759654\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158270/extras/GifHome.gif?t=1733759654\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158270/extras/Fridge.gif?t=1733759654\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158270/extras/GifGym.gif?t=1733759654\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Comprehensive Career Mode: Start your football career from scratch and reach the top.<br></li><li>Detailed Economic System: Manage your earnings, control your expenses, and make investments.<br></li><li>TV, Radio, and Magazine Content: Relax at home with various TV channels, radio programs, and magazines.<br></li><li>Relationship Management: Build friendships and romances by managing your relationships with NPCs.<br></li><li>Press Conferences: Boost your reputation by answering questions during press conferences.<br></li><li>Gambling and Entertainment: Try your luck at casinos and other entertainment activities to increase your earnings.<br></li><li>Injuries and Treatment: Manage treatment processes in case of injuries and fight to return to the field.<br></li><li>Match Fights: Get involved in fights during matches and deal with the consequences.<br></li><li>Home Decoration: Use your earnings to decorate and personalize your living space.<br></li><li>Character Customization: Customize your character's appearance and style to create a unique football player.<br></li><li>Pets: Adopt pets and take care of them, adding a special touch to your social life.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb